This Dokuwiki plugin automatically copies new users in a dokuwiki installation to a Zenphoto user database. When a user's details change, the changes are applied to Zenphotos user database too. It provides a single sign on mechanism as well.

Requirements:
  * Zenphoto installation
  * Dokuwiki installation

Usage:
  * Unzip to your Dokuwiki lib/plugins directory
  * Login to your Dokuwiki and visit your admin page
  * Edit zenlogin options according to your Zenphoto configuration
  * Register user and watch them appear in your Zenphoto installation

This plugin is (obviously) based on https://github.com/falstaff84/dokuwiki-zenphoto
which is unfortunately not maintained any more.